1. When creating code use the Rubocop linting rules.

2. When checking for linting errors always use RuboCop. 
If there are any errors rerun RuboCop and pass in autocorrect flag of "-a"
Example: "bundle exec rubocop -a spec/controllers/lnurl_callback_controller_spec.rb"